         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"The white plaster with rose oil: 1 drachma of fresh young pig fat, one-fourth ounce of litharge, one-fourth ounce ounce of birthwort Longa, one-fourth ounce of wax, one-fourth drachma of myrrh, 5 ounces of oil, the whites of three cooked eggs. Prepare and use."</ab>
